author: philip
msg: Fix a bug reported by plasma <plasma@ms9.hinet.net>, a wc-to-wc directory
move or copy could fail as it passed paths that were not in the native
encoding to the native-to-utf8 conversion function.
* subversion/libsvn_subr/io.c (svn_io_copy_dir_recursively): Do native
to UTF-8 conversion only on the entry name.

author: maxb
msg: Buildsystem: M4 changequote is nasty, and the autoconf manual reviles it.
Stop using it. Simple quoting does the job just as well.
* configure.in:
* build/ac-macros/berkeley-db.m4:
* build/ac-macros/svn-macros.m4:
* build/ac-macros/neon.m4:
Use [quotes], not changequote().

author: maxb
msg: commit-email.pl: Temporary directory handling changes.
